These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There 2 different types of food: blueberry, lettuce
There are 2 different nationalities: thai, spanish
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, havana
The people have 2 different hobbies: rock-climbing, camping
1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the havana-smoker##3
2. the person eating lettuce is in an even position##4
3. the spanish is the person eating blueberry##1
4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Food      | blueberry  | lettuce   |
| Nationality   | spanish     | thai   |
| Cigar         | havana | fonseca |
| Hobby     | rock-climbing | camping    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
City: paris, miami
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, october
The people have 2 different jobs:  writer, photographer
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: aconite, iris
1. the photographer is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in november is the person who growsiris##1
3. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| City          | paris     | miami |
| Birthday   | october | november  |
| Job           | photographer         | writer     |
| Flower     | aconite   | iris    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
City: hamburg, miami
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, snowboarding
2 different games are played: billiard, backgammon
House: palace, cape-cod
1. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
2. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
3. the person traveling to hamburg is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| City    | miami     | hamburg |
| Sport         | snowboarding | rugby    |
| Game         | billiard         | backgammon        |
| House   | palace         | cape-cod    |

