The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: aconite, rose
2 different pets are kept: rat, dog
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: western, horror
1. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
2. the person who growsrose is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
3. the person watching horror movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Cigar      | tiparillo     | cain |
| Flower          | rose   | aconite  |
| Pet         | rat | dog     |
| Movie-Genre   | western  | horror         |

