.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, cooking
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: trance, country
There are 2 different favourite colors: grey, light-blue
There 2 different types of food: cabbage, kiwi
1. the person eating kiwi is in an even position##4
2. the fan of country is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is the fan of trance##1
4. the person who likes grey is on the left of the fan of country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Hobby           | cooking | board-games    |
| Music-Genre   | trance       | country |
| Color           | grey         | light-blue    |
| Food         | cabbage    | kiwi   |

