1. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the tiparillo-smoker##3
2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the person playing chess is in an even position##4
4. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |        2        |
