The people prefer 2 different music-genres: salsa, ambient
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: october, march
2 different games are played: whist, snooker
1. the fan of ambient is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the turkish##3
3. the person playing whist is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Nationality    | dutch | turkish    |
| Music-Genre         | ambient        | salsa |
| Birthday         | october          | march     |
| Game   | whist        | snooker     |

 